cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IT, cs.DS, cs.ST

This paper is about a machine learning algorithm (Thompson Sampling) and its regret analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IT (Information Theory). The paper also uses martingale-based analysis techniques, which are commonly used in probability theory and stochastic processes, suggesting that cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.ST (Statistics) are also possible categories.
